    title: "Introduction",
    content: "WELCOME TO NYX NEURAL REGISTRY.\nMISSION: Data retrieval for Blessed Access.\nCORE MOTTO: 'LOVE OF GOD, LOVE OF COUNTRY, ABOVE ALL'"
  },
  OATH: {
    title: "Oath of Membership",
    content: "OATH OF MEMBERSHIP:\n'I, having been accepted as member of BLESSED MOVEMENT, INC. do solemnly and sincerely promised and swear that I will faithfully support, abide by, enforce, and defend the Constitution of the Republic of the Philippines and all laws and legal orders promulgated by the duly constituted authorities and the Constitution, By-Laws and Rules and Regulations of BLESSED MOVEMENT, INC... FOR THE LOVE OF GOD, LOVE OF COUNTRY, ABOVE ALL. SO, HELP ME GOD.'"
  },
  "6_AREAS": {
    title: "6 Personal Areas of Success (Book 1)",
    content: "THE 6 PERSONAL AREAS OF SUCCESS (BOOK 1):\n1. Physical: Health, Wellness, Vitality.\n2. Intellectual: Knowledge, Wisdom, Lifelong Learning.\n3. Emotional: Stability, Peace, Resilience.\n4. Social: Relationships, Community Standing.\n5. Financial: Freedom, Savings, Stewardship.\n6. Spiritual: Faith, Alignment with God."
  },
  "6_LEVELS": {
    title: "6 Organizational Levels",
    content: "THE 6 ORGANIZATIONAL FOCUS LEVELS:\n1. Barangay\n2. Municipal/City\n3. Provincial\n4. Regional\n5. National\n6. Global"
  },
  "4_WAYS_TO_EARN": {
    title: "4 Ways to Earn in Life (Book 2)",
    content: "THE 4 WAYS TO EARN IN LIFE (E, B, S, I - BOOK 2):\n1. EMPLOYEE (E): Trades time for money. 95% population / 5% wealth. Stress, no security, no time.\n2. BUSINESS OWNER (B): Owns a system. 5% population / 95% wealth. Passive income, stability, time.\n3. SELF-EMPLOYED (S): Owns a job. Small business, large debts, insufficient funds.\n4. INVESTOR (I): Money works for you. No debts, financial freedom, wealth multiplication."
  },
  "7_STEPS": {
    title: "7 Steps to Success Strategy (Book 2)",
    content: "THE 7 STEPS TO SUCCESS STRATEGY (BOOK 2):\n1. GOAL: The Foundation. Define exactly what you want.\n2. EFFORT: Hard work and persistence.\n3. UNITY: Strength in numbers; stronger as a group.\n4. ATTENTION: Focus and vigilance.\n5. RESPECT: For the system and each other.\n6. COMMUNICATION: Clear channels and honesty.\n7. GLOBAL GOALS: Reaching national and international impact."
  },
  FINANCIAL_FORMULA: {
    title: "Financial Planning Formula",
    content: "FINANCIAL PLANNING FORMULA:\n(Total Dreams to Goals Cost) / (Number of Working Days) = Average Income Per Day required.\nRequires tracking of Target vs. Actual Quarterly Income and Variance analysis."
